# Build output

This project bundles split UI via `scripts/build-ui.mjs` into `ui.html` and compiles the plugin host with `tsc` into `code.js`.

- From the repository root, run **`npm run build`** after changing anything that affects those outputs, including:
  - `ui/**/*.js`, `ui.css`, or other inputs used by the UI build
  - `code.ts` or any file covered by `tsconfig.json`
- When you finish a task that touches those areas, run the build yourself; do not only tell the user to run it unless the environment cannot execute npm.
